bilingual.target: 他使用最新的计算机技术。

bilingual.source: Every issue is packed from cover to cover with the latest stories.
bilingual.target: 每一期都从头到尾充满了最新的故事。

bilingual.source: We collect the latest national and international news and write reports here.
bilingual.target: 我们在这里收集最新的国内外新闻并撰写报道。

bilingual.source: Come and watch the latest films, enjoy them with your friends, talk about them.
bilingual.target: 来看最新的电影，和朋友们一起享受，讨论它们。

bilingual.source: These adverts have been written to appeal to girls, while the adverts for boys are more likely to be for the latest console or computer game.
bilingual.target: 这些广告是为了吸引女孩，而男孩的广告更可能是最新的游戏机或电脑游戏。
我买了一张他们最新的专辑。
你看过她最新的帖子吗？
你看过那部最新的电影了吗？
我们可以读取最新的报告吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I've checked the latest reports. We're clear all the way to Charlotte.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看了最新的预报，我们到夏洛特是畅通无阻的。

yingyinNormal.en: So, tell me about your scalar dark energy experiment. Not 'til you tell me about your latest paper on quantum loop theory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟我说说你的标量场暗能量实验。你先跟我说说你最新的论文圈量子理论。

yingyinNormal.en: What do you need that kind of money for? I have figured out an experimental design that may corroborate my latest thinking on string theory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要这么大一笔钱干什么啊？我想出了一个实验设计可以证实我最新的弦理论想法。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you. Robert, what's the latest on the omnibus?
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢。罗伯特，福利改革怎么样了？

yingyinNormal.en: Now if you'll excuse me, the latest issue of batman is out. Come, Leonard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在请允许我失陪了，新一期蝙蝠侠出版了，走吧，莱纳德。

yingyinNormal.en: Get anything good? Just the latest copy of applied particle physics quarterly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有什么好东西吗？最近一季度的应用粒子物理学报。

yingyinNormal.en: But even LAMOST will soon be dwarfed by one of China's latest engineering marvel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而即使是郭守敬望远镜很快也会在中国最新一项工程奇迹面前相形见绌。

yingyinNormal.en: Our latest probe images will give you an idea of what's happening on the enemy planet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们最近的探测图像能让你明白，敌对星球上正发生的事。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, hello. Oh, sorry I'm late. I just got so caught up reading the draft of your latest paper.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好。抱歉，我来晚了，我赶着看你最新论文的草稿来着。

yingyinNormal.en: All of them. I thought the latest was brilliant, God's Cauldron. You read that? In one sitting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 都读过，我觉得你的新书很精彩，《上帝之釜》。你读过了？一口气读完的。

yingyinNormal.en: The focus of his latest experiment was the oldest light in the universe. The faint afterglow of the big bang.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他最新实验关注的就是宇宙中最古老的光。大爆炸的微弱余辉。

yingyinNormal.en: Balem, thank you for responding. We were just admiring this ledger from your latest success. Well done, brother.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜蓝，谢谢你的回答。空荡荡的没有人啊，我们正在赞赏你最近取得的突出成绩。干得不错，哥哥。

yingyinNormal.en: So if we could leave at 8:00, we'd still be able to regain our birthright at 10:00, 10:30 latest. Fine. Leonard?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我们我们8点出发，我们还能在10点最晚10:30重获我们的权利。行，莱纳德？

yingyinNormal.en: It came together for me after Alex intercepted the Shop's latest shipment, four Pakistani men, all the same physical type.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾丽克丝最近截获一批"商店"的货物，是四个巴基斯坦人时，我就想明白了，他们体型完全相同。

yingyinNormal.en: I was thinking specifically of the gentleman over there moving his lips as he enjoys the latest exploits of Betty and Veronica.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想到了那边那位念念有词欣赏最新《贝蒂和维罗妮卡》的先生。

yingyinNormal.en: And Paul Franklin and his team, they were thrilled to get algorithms that were the absolute latest, most interesting and up-to-the-minute.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而保罗富兰克林和他的团队，他们很激动能获得算法，它们绝对是最新最有趣的算法。

yingyinNormal.en: I want you to work up something for my latest frozen food concept. Gusteau's Corn Puppies. They're like corn dogs, only smaller. Bite size.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要你替我的冷冻食品想些新花样, 食神的油炸玉米狗, 样子就像炸热狗，不过小一点一口就可以吃掉。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a whole new story about our Earth told through remarkable images, captured for the very first time, and the latest scientific discoveries.
yingyinNormal.zh: 植物掀开了地球史上一页崭新篇章我将用这些前所未有的一幕幕精彩画面，及最新科学发现讲述植物的故事。

yingyinNormal.en: And here is what he's so excited about. It's America's newest auto plant, a billion-dollar state-of-the-art facility filled with all of the latest technology.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是他非常兴奋的一点，这是美国最先进的汽车化计划，价值大约十亿，配备了最先进的科技成果。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, so, while I am powerpointing, you know, and citing the latest legislation, she's flipping her hair and giggling at the client, and her cleavage is like a whole other person in the room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我做幻灯片（PPT），引用最新立法的时候，她却抚着头发和客户嬉笑，还有她春光乍现的乳沟。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: newest or most recent or modern

examination_example.sentence: We strongly intend to continue this dialogue, including talks with Greenpeace, to discuss improvements based on the <highlight>latest</highlight> scientific data.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们强烈希望继续这一对话，包括与绿色和平组织的对话，讨论基于最新科学数据上的改进。

examination_example.sentence: That is why we welcome Mr. Musk's <highlight>latest</highlight> venture, and wish him well.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是为什么我们欢迎 Musk 先生的最新尝试，并祝他一切顺利。

sense_info_list.en: newest or most recent or modern

examination_example.sentence: Many people in Paris were eager to have a look at the <highlight>latest</highlight> sweet food made by Creme.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 巴黎的许多人都渴望一睹由Creme制作的最新甜食。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>latest</highlight> in cat research reveals that the lovely animal seems to have a basic grasp on both the laws of physics and the ins and outs of cause and effect.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最新的猫咪研究显示，可爱的动物似乎对物理定律和因果关系的来龙去脉都有基本的掌握。

examination_example.sentence: The findings of the <highlight>latest</highlight> research were similar to an earlier multi-state study of assisted living.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这项最新研究的结果与早先的一项关于辅助生活的多状态研究相似。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: newest or most recent or modern

examination_example.sentence: Susanna Reid is used to grilling guests on the sofa every morning, but she is cooking up a storm in her <highlight>latest</highlight> role.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Susanna Reid已经习惯了每天早上在沙发上采访嘉宾，但她最近的角色是煮得一手好菜。

examination_example.sentence: I enjoyed studying different kinds of cars and planes, playing pop music, and collecting the <highlight>latest</highlight> music albums.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我喜欢研究各种各样的汽车和飞机、播放流行音乐以及收集最新的音乐专辑。

examination_example.sentence: A <highlight>latest</highlight> study on the college job market showed that employers wanted to hire 22% fewer graduates this year than last.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项关于大学就业市场的最新研究显示，雇主今年希望招聘的毕业生比去年减少了22%。
